<sect2 id="sect_definingCharts" label="7">
    <title id="title_definingCharts">Defining charts in a form</title>
    <informaltable frame="none">
        <tgroup rowsep="0" cols="2" align="left" colsep="0">
            <colspec colwidth="1*"/>
            <colspec colwidth="3*"/>
            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry rowsep="1"/>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Purpose</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>Additional to <glossterm linkend=" DBElement">DB elements</glossterm>,
                                <glossterm linkend=" normalElement">normal elements</glossterm> and
                            buttons the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> designer offers the possibility
                            to add charts to form. </para>
                        <para>These charts can graphically illustrate e.g. measurement readings or
                            statistical values stored in a table field of the type binary and are
                            like <glossterm linkend=" normalElement">normal elements</glossterm>
                            controlled by <glossterm linkend="GUIHook">GUI hooks</glossterm>.</para>
                        <para>You can choose between the following chart presentation types:</para>
                        <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <guilabel>Line Chart</guilabel> and</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <guilabel>Bar Chart</guilabel>.</para>
                            </listitem>
                        </itemizedlist>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Hot spots</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>In comparison to line charts bar charts enable also to define hot spots.</para>
                        <para>ADD more information here!!!!</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Procedure</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para> Proceed the following steps to define a chart in a group:</para>
                        <para>
                            <informaltable rowsep="1" colsep="1" frame="all">
                                <tgroup cols="2">
                                    <colspec align="center" colwidth="1*"/>
                                    <colspec align="left" colwidth="6*"/>
                                    <thead>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>Step</entry>
                                            <entry align="center">Procedure</entry>
                                        </row>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>1</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Load the form containing the group to be
                                                  edited into the form editor.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>2</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Select the desired chart type from the
                                                  <guibutton>Charts</guibutton> menu in the form editor.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>3</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>Place the button at the desired position in
                                                  the group by pressing the left mouse button.</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                        <row>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para>4</para>
                                            </entry>
                                            <entry>
                                                <para> Create an event handler and implement the
                                                  appropriate methods as described in the section
                                                  ....ADD link to section!!!....</para>
                                            </entry>
                                        </row>
                                    </tbody>
                                </tgroup>
                            </informaltable>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry/>
                    <entry/>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </informaltable>
</sect2>
